<br>
You are basically going to have an alignment system (although a simple one) no matter what server you are on.  You might still be able to group with each other but since guilds and families swear allegiance to a city and your guild hall would be in this city, I imagine it would be hard or even impossible to have a guild that contains both good and evil characters.<br>
<br>
TLC also seems to be a non issue as if I remember correctly there will be item decay.  I imagine this system will replace both TLC and no drop.<br>
<br>
Seems to me like all EQ2 servers will have a bit of that old FV feeling to them.<br>
